latestIgtvVideos.caption:
KAYRA!!!!!!!
LESSSSSSSS GOOOOOO!!!!!
I dont really have words to describe what Kayra gave me- confidence , positivity,self love, n especially A FAMILY!! 
Leaving Kayra was one of the  toughestttt decision I have ever made. I never thought I will miss crying while doing planks, JAO EXTRA ROUNDS DAUD KE AO, "vaapis se first position m lgo", "haath thight rkho na subh workout nhi kiya?" and so much more! I really miss going to Khwahish di for every small trouble only to hear "Arey Koini Hojayega Bachee",
Vanshita Di's patience, Deepali Di's perfectionism (nhi ye step aise ni aise hai BETA SMJH NHI AARI), Chanchal Di's calmness And Gurleen Di's Strength.
I miss hanging out w all the first years because WHY NOT! All those side eyes we passed when we used to get a "dubara kro" from seniors 🙂 words cannot explain what I'm feeling rn. ILY guys so much !!

@kayradancesoc

N Thanksssss @simyayyyy for helping with the caption😌
